---
import { BadgeCheck } from "lucide-react";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
    class="mt-24 lg:mt-40 bg-sheet-white border border-sheet-border p-8 lg:p-16 technical-sheet-shadow rounded-sm"
>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
        <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
            <h3
                class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-black uppercase text-slate-ink border-l-[4px] lg:border-l-[6px] border-accent-orange pl-4 lg:pl-6 tracking-tight"
            >
                Ramy Prawne
            </h3>
            <p
                class="text-[10px] lg:text-[11px] font-mono text-slate-ink/80 leading-relaxed font-medium"
            >
                Wszystkie schematy techniczne i dane architektoniczne
                prezentowane w tym archiwum pozostają wyłączną własnością
                intelektualną firmy Dachy Tarnów. Jakiekolwiek powielanie lub
                cytowanie musi zawierać identyfikator archiwum: DT-TRN-2024.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
            <h3
                class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-black uppercase text-slate-ink border-l-[4px] lg:border-l-[6px] border-accent-orange pl-4 lg:pl-6 tracking-tight"
            >
                Wsparcie Archiwum
            </h3>
            <div
                class="font-mono text-[10px] lg:text-[11px] space-y-3 lg:space-y-4 text-slate-ink"
            >
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="opacity-60">EMAIL:</span>
                    <span
                        class="text-slate-ink font-bold hover:text-accent-orange transition-colors cursor-pointer"
                        >archiwum@dachytarnow.pl</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="opacity-60">TELEFON:</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-ink font-bold"
                        >+48 14 600 00 00</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                    <span class="opacity-60">DOSTĘPNOŚĆ:</span>
                    <span class="text-slate-ink font-bold"
                        >Poniedziałek - Sobota</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-l-0 md:border-l border-sheet-border pt-8 md:pt-0 md:pl-16"
        >
            <div
                class="w-24 h-24 lg:w-32 lg:h-32 border-2 border-slate-ink p-2 lg:p-3 mb-4 lg:mb-6 relative flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-50/50 shadow-inner hover:rotate-5 hover:scale-105 transition-all"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-1 border-dashed border border-slate-ink/30"
                >
                </div>
                <BadgeCheck
                    className="text-slate-ink"
                    size={48}
                    strokeWidth={1.5}
                />
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-mono text-[9px] lg:text-[10px] text-center text-slate-ink uppercase tracking-[0.15em] lg:tracking-[0.2em] font-bold"
            >
                Gwarancja Jakości
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="mt-12 lg:mt-16 pt-8 lg:pt-10 border-t border-sheet-border flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-[9px] lg:text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-ink/40 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-center md:text-left"
    >
        <span>© {year} SzramaDach. Wszystkie prawa zastrzeżone.</span>
    </div>
</footer>
